To help promote the work, he'll play a West Coast swing in late October that will visit Las Vegas and Los Angeles before closing at Oakland's Fox Theater on October 27. We could make a never-ending list of Knopfler's accomplishments, but we'll tie it up by noting he's also recorded and produced seven solo albums, composed and produced scores for eight films, and had the chance to work with some of the world's most prominent musicians.
